{"tid":1131733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港政客失敗原因：反共產黨但又最中意實踐毛澤東思想","createTime":"2019-04-30T00:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T11:26:25.000Z","uid":20816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0f00081727b80af127ed2cc4d242c0fbedd03d","tid":1131733,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:26:48.000Z","msg":"咩「敵人嘅敵人就係朋友」、「團結次要敵人打擊主要敵人」<br />\n跟住同「敵人嘅敵人」、「次要敵人」一齊嫖妓、做壞事、仲當佢係神父：將自己畢生做過嘅壞事向佢哋傾訴<br />\n結果係主要敵人未打敗，自己就已經被「敵人嘅敵人」同「次要敵人」揸住痛腳或搞到身敗名裂<br />\n而香港市民對別人嘅道德標準要求又高（封建時代同中東地區都無咁高）<br />\n睇住一個又一個有機會帶領香港嘅人中箭落馬<br />\n各位有志拯救香港嘅年青人<br />\n希望你哋小心<br />\n前車可鑑"},{"pid":"f50a5beebb259aae66b30a50c2e3b2c3e2c81c8b","tid":1131733,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:35:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">老鳳完全認同</span></span>"},{"pid":"abb59f7785672199080a60510ca6791d8e72f707","tid":1131733,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f50a5beebb259aae66b30a50c2e3b2c3e2c81c8b","tid":1131733,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:35:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">老鳳完全認同</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5825b4d745eb45b0b6227ab918a4e633869d7f","tid":1131733,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}